aspguidp.exception

Class InvalidEntityRepresentationException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • aspguidp.exception.InvalidEntityRepresentationException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class InvalidEntityRepresentationException
extends java.lang.Exception
    Signals that a given string value or a given placeholder value map is not a string representation of an Entity. This exception is thrown, if the conversion of a string value or a placeholder map to an entity fails.
